Trends and Active Areas
Evidence Synthesis: Proliferation of systematic reviews, meta-analyses, umbrella reviews, evidence maps (e.g., on acupuncture, medical cannabis, specific practices), and bibliometric studies. Many focus on pain, cancer supportive care, mental health, musculoskeletal issues, and chronic disease. 

hsrd.research.va.gov +1

Whole-Person and Multimodal Approaches: Shift from single-modality studies to complex interventions, real-world implementation, and outcomes like resilience, interoception, and health promotion.
